Package edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.stack

Class LinkedStack<E>

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.stack.AbstractStack<E>
edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.stack.LinkedStack<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements stored in the stack
All Implemented Interfaces:
Stack<E>
public class LinkedStack<E> extends AbstractStack<E>
The Linked Stack is implemented as a singly-linked list data structure to support efficient, O(1) worst-case Stack abstract data type behaviors.
Author:
Dr. King, Jeremiah Knizley
